body: "Add an integration test in cli.integration.spec.ts that:\\n1. Creates items with draft/open/in_progress/blocked/closed/canceled statuses\\n2. Runs pm list (bare command)\\n3. Verifies closed and canceled items are NOT present\\n4. Verifies draft/open/in_progress/blocked items ARE present"
